Actions.Text: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

Title: Establishes the city of Buffalo parking authority
Summary: Establishes the city of Buffalo parking authority; provides for its powers, duties and obligations.
LawCode: Add Art 7 Title 5 §§1500-a - 1500-w, Pub Auth L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public authorities law, in relation to establishing the city of Buffalo parking authority
